### Create a new Category
POST https://ecom-api-lcxh.onrender.com/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Furniture",
  "description": "Tables, chairs, sofas and home furniture"
}

### Create a new Product (replace category ID with the one from the response above)
POST https://ecom-api-lcxh.onrender.com/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luxury Sofa",
  "description": "Premium leather sofa with recliner",
  "price": 2500.00,
  "stock": 8,
  "category": "6918a676a851b8c8f2ca0680",
  "weight": 45000,
  "dimensions": "200x90x95 cm"
}

